  <title>CAMBODIA: Admin Level 1 Boundaries</title>
  <abstract>The dataset represents the provinces and capital of Cambodia. The dataset was obtained from the Department of Geography of the Ministry of Land Management, Urbanization and Construction in 2008 and unofficially updated in 2014 according to sub-decrees on administrative modifications. Data provided by WFP - VAM unit Cambodia.

Cambodia administrative level 1 (province/khaet and capital/reach thani) boundary.</abstract>

  <history>Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase. The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Found and fixed 2 Gap Errors. 2. Found and fixed small nesting errors with other admin layers. 3. Projection changed from undefined to 'GCS_WGS_1984'. </history>
